{"id": "8048", "post": "<div class=\"post-8048 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers category-new-provider tag-canada tag-kvm tag-ssd tag-windows tag-xsroute-com\" id=\"post-8048\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/xsroute-1gb-kvm-vps-6-50mo-for-windows-or-4-30mo-for-linux-in-canada/\" rel=\"bookmark\">XSRoute \u2013 1GB KVM VPS, $6.50/mo for Windows or $4.30/mo for Linux in Canada</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/canada/\" rel=\"tag\">canada</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/kvm/\" rel=\"tag\">kvm</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/ssd/\" rel=\"tag\">ssd</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/windows/\" rel=\"tag\">windows</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xsroute-com/\" rel=\"tag\">xsroute.com</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> December 12, 2015 @ 1:00 pm, by Jonathan Tan</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://www.xsroute.com\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIzMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTYwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMzAwIDE2MCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot alignnone size-medium wp-image-6315\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/xsroute-300x160.png.webp\" alt=\"XSRoute\" width=\"300\" height=\"160\"></a></p><p>David, from <a href=\"https://www.xsroute.com/\">XSRoute</a>, sent us their first offer for the LowEndBox community. This offer uses the KVM virtualization with SSD storage for performance. Linux and Windows are supported and the servers are located in Canada with OVH. Take note that IPv6 and BitCoins are not supported.</p><p>Host node for this offer has Intel Xeon D-1520, 128GB RAM, 8x 800GB SSD in Hardware RAID10 and a 1Gbps uplink. The CPU seems promising and the 8 SSD drives should give good performance.</p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>KVM SSD Linux \u2013 1GB</strong><p></p><ul><li>1024MB RAM</li><li>1024MB Swap</li><li>2x vCPU</li><li>20GB SSD space</li><li>1TB transfer</li><li>100Mbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>KVM/Virtualizor</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEB1GB</strong></li><li>$4.30/month</li><li><a href=\"https://www.xsroute.com/portal/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=7\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>KVM SSD Windows \u2013 1GB</strong><p></p><ul><li>1024MB RAM</li><li>2x vCPU</li><li>25GB SSD space</li><li>1TB transfer</li><li>100Mbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>KVM/Virtualizor</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEB1GBWIN</strong></li><li>$6.50/month</li><li><a href=\"https://www.xsroute.com/portal/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=12\">Order here</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>XSRoute Inc is a group of people working as System Administrators since 2005 and registered as a company in late 2006. They initially offered services to limited companies and individuals while not yet being online. They are now providing service to the general public. Their website was created last 2006 but WHOIS is not public. They are a registered company with registration number 47-5135450. I was unable to find any reviews on the Internet and we would appreciate if you will share your experiences below.</p><p><span id=\"more-8048\"></span></p><p>PayPal aand 2Checkout are the only supported payment methods. Reading their Terms of Service seems to indicate that refunds is only available with their shared and reseller products only. As always, we strongly encourage our readers to review their <a href=\"https://www.xsroute.com/tos.php\">Terms of Service</a> carefully before making any purchase.</p><p><strong>Network information</strong></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">OVH \u2013 Monteral, Canada </span><br>\nTest IPv4: 158.69.224.17</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fxsroute-1gb-kvm-vps-6-50mo-for-windows-or-4-30mo-for-linux-in-canada%2F&amp;t=XSRoute%20-%201GB%20KVM%20VPS%2C%20%246.50%2Fmo%20for%20Windows%20or%20%20%244.30%2Fmo%20for%20Linux%20in%20Canada\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=XSRoute%20-%201GB%20KVM%20VPS%2C%20%246.50%2Fmo%20for%20Windows%20or%20%20%244.30%2Fmo%20for%20Linux%20in%20Canada&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fxsroute-1gb-kvm-vps-6-50mo-for-windows-or-4-30mo-for-linux-in-canada%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fxsroute-1gb-kvm-vps-6-50mo-for-windows-or-4-30mo-for-linux-in-canada%2F&amp;title=XSRoute%20-%201GB%20KVM%20VPS%2C%20%246.50%2Fmo%20for%20Windows%20or%20%20%244.30%2Fmo%20for%20Linux%20in%20Canada&amp;mini=true\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-linkedin dpsp-no-label dpsp-last\